Milvus Haystack component requires a running Milvus server instance.

The docker-compose.yaml provides a hopefully straight-forward way to start one locally.
This is then accessible at `http://localhost:19530/default`.

In this directory, run
```bash
mkdir ~/docker-volumes
export DOCKER_VOLUME_DIRECTORY=~/docker-volumes
chmod +rw $DOCKER_VOLUME_DIRECTORY
```
and then,
```
docker compose up
```
